{"article_id":"5CSGUPqD8SAyzW0G","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The FBI Is Going To Investigate Kavanaugh After All .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"What Does That Mean ?","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"A wild turn of events on Friday flipped a new FBI investigation into Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh from a long shot into a sure thing .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"That was one result of an eleventh-hour agreement among the members of the Senate Judiciary Committee after a contentious session of offstage horse-trading .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"The panel voted to recommend the embattled Kavanaugh to the full Senate on the condition","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that the final floor vote not take place","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"until after the FBI conducted a background investigation into allegations of sexual misconduct","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"confronting the nominee .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"The inquiry would be `` limited in scope ''","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"and completed within a week .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"The White House later Friday ordered the bureau to do just that .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"The FBI is expected to produce a report for the White House ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"which the administration would then give the Senate .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Democrats and outside groups had been calling for the FBI 's involvement","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"since the allegations by Christine Blasey Ford and other women first surfaced","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"that Kavanaugh had assaulted them","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"or committed other such acts","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"- allegations","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that Kavanaugh strongly denies .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Sen. Jeff Flake , R-Ariz. , pitched the delay and new investigation to his compatriots ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"apparently setting that as his condition","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"for ultimately supporting Kavanaugh on the Senate floor .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Republican leaders ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"who need every vote","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"they can get","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"to confirm the nominee ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"agreed .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Judiciary Committee Chairman Chuck Grassley , R-Iowa , had opposed involving the FBI","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"but said Friday","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"he would take up Flake 's case .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Ultimately he secured an agreement with Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , R-Ky .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"`` We 've had a good day today","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"by moving the nominee , ''","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"Grassley told reporters .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"`` A good day .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"We 're very happy with the progress","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"we 've made . ''","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"it will be better for the country","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"that this FBI investigation occur , ''","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"Sen. Amy Klobuchar , D-Minn. , told NPR .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"`` I 'm not sure","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"what the answers will be .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"It 's possible some of the witnesses wo n't even agree to talk with FBI . ...","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"But to think","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"we would n't even try","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"would be the saddest thing for the country . ''","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"The new deadline for a Kavanaugh vote is Oct. 5 .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"Grassley asked President Trump to instruct the FBI to spend that week","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"conducting interviews ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"reviewing documents","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"and looking into the new accusations .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"`` The supplemental FBI background investigation would be limited to current credible allegations against the nominee","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"and must be completed no later than one week from today , ''","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Grassley said .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"It was n't immediately clear whether `` current credible allegations '' would mean","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"the FBI would interview only people","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"connected with Ford 's case or with some of the other women","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"who have come forward with allegations against Kavanaugh .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"The FBI is unlikely to open a criminal investigation .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Instead , its investigators are expected to pursue the same kind of background inquiry","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"they have conducted on Kavanaugh in the past ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"focused on the new allegations .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"The nominee said in a statement","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"released by the White House","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"that he would go along .","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"`` Throughout this process , I 've been interviewed by the FBI ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"I 've done a number of 'background ' calls directly with the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"and yesterday , I answered questions under oath about every topic","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"the Senators and their counsel asked me , ''","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Kavanaugh said .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"`` I 've done everything","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"they have requested","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"and will continue to cooperate . ''","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"At least one key player in this drama also volunteered to talk :","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"Mark Judge","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"- a boyhood friend of Kavanaugh 's","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"who has been accused by Ford of being a bystander to her sexual assault","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"and was named in other allegations -","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"said in a letter to the Judiciary Committee","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"that he would cooperate under certain conditions .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Judge renewed his denials","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"about being involved with any sexual misconduct","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"that he would `` cooperate with any law enforcement agency","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that is assigned to confidentially investigate these allegations . ''","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"It 's a crime to lie to Congress ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"but lying to the FBI is a whole other matter .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"And there is a practical difference","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"between people in the Kavanaugh case issuing written statements","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"- as Judge and others have done -","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"and actually sitting down with human special agents .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"Investigators might glean details from people involved","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"that are n't yet in the public eye .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"They might discover","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"there are more people ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"including witnesses or others ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"than have been a part of the public accounting so far .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"But the FBI will not give its own determination about the truthfulness of what witnesses say - one reason","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"Grassley and Kavanaugh both earlier said","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"they opposed activating the bureau .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Investigators probably only will conduct interviews","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"and then pass them to the Senate ,","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"they said .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"Even if the bureau serves only as a gold-plated transcription service in this case ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"the completeness of those transcripts might exceed the body of evidence","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"that now exists","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"- and it would be evidence","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"obtained from witnesses","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"who could be prosecuted","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"if they lied to the feds .","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"Democrats and outside groups","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"- and now , Flake -","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"argue","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"that the information","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"that has surfaced recently","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"means the FBI must look into Kavanaugh again .","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"Ford told the Judiciary Committee","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"she had n't told anyone about her alleged sexual assault by the 1990s ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"when Kavanaugh was screened for a job in the Justice Department ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"or even by the early 2000s ,","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"when he was cleared to work in the White House of President George W. Bush .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"Many Republicans say","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"the due diligence on Kavanaugh already was complete .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"Now that the Judiciary Committee has voted to recommend him to the full Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"they argue ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"the full chamber must decide .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":253,"left":128,"right":252,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":172,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":138,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":129,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":134,"right":136,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":134,"left":132,"